    "The models will then be fine-tuned and trained on the target dataset of shoulder tasks.",
    "Our method guarantees that the models learn relevant features, as both the source of TL and the target task use the same image modality (X-ray) and share the same aim of abnormality detection.",
    "It also reduces the need for annotated images of the target task.",
    "The source of TL can be time-efficient unannotated images.",
    "Seven pre-trained models trained with and without the proposed TL were employed."
